# 규칙 정의: docs/process/governance.md §2.7
#
# 설치:
#   cp scripts/hooks/pre-commit .git/hooks/pre-commit && chmod +x .git/hooks/pre-commit
#
# 게이트:
#   1. document-sync (모든 commit)
#   2. python-tests (harness/tests/agents/yml staged 시만)

